      "line": 42,
      "message": "Unfortunately, this is too generic. There is no such thing from a user's perspective as \"item\", or \"version\". There is a \"VSP\", for example, or \"VSP Version\". Preferable even \"VSP 'Test'\" and \"Version 1.0 of VSP 'Test'\"",
